---
import BaseHead from '../../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
import Header from '../../components/Header.astro';
import { SITE_TITLE } from '../../consts';

const chapters = [
  { year: 2026, title: 'Local-first AI / 本地优先的 AI', href: '/blog/volumes/vol-open-2026-2029/2026-chapter-47-local-first-ai/' },
  { year: 2027, title: 'Multimodal normalization / 多模态常态化', href: '/blog/volumes/vol-open-2026-2029/2027-chapter-48-multimodal-normalization/' },
  { year: 2028, title: 'Governance of models / 模型治理', href: '/blog/volumes/vol-open-2026-2029/2028-chapter-49-governance-of-models/' },
  { year: 2029, title: 'The half-era becomes visible / 0.5 纪元变得可见', href: '/blog/volumes/vol-open-2026-2029/2029-chapter-50-the-half-era-becomes-visible/' },
];
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <BaseHead
      title={`${SITE_TITLE} · Open Volume`}
      description="Open volume notes for 2026-2029: a forward line kept intentionally open while the period is still unfolding."
    />
    <style>
      .hero,
      .section {
        padding: 1.35rem 1.45rem;
        border-radius: 22px;
        border: 1px solid rgba(var(--line), 0.8);
        background: rgba(255,255,255,0.76);
        box-shadow: var(--box-shadow);
      }
      .hero + .section,
      .section + .section {
        margin-top: 1.2rem;
      }
      .eyebrow {
        margin: 0 0 0.5rem;
        color: rgb(var(--gray));
        text-transform: uppercase;
        letter-spacing: 0.08em;
        font-size: 0.85rem;
      }
      .lead {
        max-width: 46rem;
      }
      .chapter-list {
        margin: 0;
        padding-left: 1.2rem;
      }
      .chapter-list li + li {
        margin-top: 0.45rem;
      }
      .muted {
        color: rgb(var(--gray));
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <Header />
    <main>
      <section class="hero">
        <p class="eyebrow">Open volume / 开放卷</p>
        <h1>2026-2029 Working Line / 2026-2029 开放线</h1>
        <p class="lead">
          This section keeps the 2026+ material visible without pretending the period is already settled.
          It is not a closed formal volume yet. It is a forward line for themes that are still unfolding in
          real time across AI, interfaces, governance, and ordinary work.
        </p>
        <p class="muted">
          这一部分把 2026 年之后的材料先公开保留下来，但不假装这个阶段已经可以被完整收口。
          它还不是正式定稿的一卷，而是一条持续展开中的前瞻线，记录 AI、界面、治理与日常工作仍在变化的现实。
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="section">
        <h2>Editorial note / 编辑说明</h2>
        <p>
          <strong>第四卷先停在 2025，是为了让已经沉淀的部分能被当作历史处理。</strong>
          2026 年之后的材料则暂时保留在这一条开放卷里，避免把仍在快速演化的现实过早写成结论。
          等这一段时间有了更稳定的边界，再决定是否收束为新的正式卷。
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="section">
        <h2>Open chapter line / 开放章节线</h2>
        <ol class="chapter-list">
          {chapters.map((chapter) => (
            <li>
              <a href={chapter.href}>{chapter.year}: {chapter.title}</a>
            </li>
          ))}
        </ol>
      </section>

      <section class="section">
        <h2>Context links / 相关入口</h2>
        <ul>
          <li><a href="/volumes/vol-4-2021-2025/">Volume IV / 第四卷</a></li>
          <li><a href="/blog/2026-03-23-volume-roadmap/">Volume roadmap / 项目卷路线图</a></li>
          <li><a href="/blog/2026-03-06-now-records-issue-1/">Now Records / 当下记录</a></li>
        </ul>
      </section>
    </main>
    <Footer />
  </body>
</html>
